721223455 +0000" stop="20260722004031 +0000" catchup-id="RUNNTV_PROGRAM_7_1784673295996_1784680831996"><title>Universal Soldier: Day Of Reckoning</title><desc>John awakens from a coma to discover his wife and daughter were murdered in a brutal home invasion. Haunted by images of the attack, he vows to kill the man responsible: The fight pits John against Andrew Scott and an army of genetically enhanced warriors; meanwhile, he must contend with a Uni Sol in relentless pursuit.</desc><date>20260721</date><icon src="https://xstreamcp-assets-msp.streamready.in/assets/RUNNTV/PROGRAM/6a5f619a527eb6ddd76addbe/images/LANDSCAPE_169/e836e9d6-f783-4d05-9ae6-da06bde44bcc.png" /></programme><programme channel="RUNNTV_LIVECHANNEL_7" start="20260722004031 +0000" stop="20260722025337 +0000" catchup-id="RUNNTV_PROGRAM_7_1784680831996_1784688817996"><title>Lawless</title><desc>We control the fear, you understand? Without the fear, we are all good as dead.&#8217; The notorious gangster Al Capone observed that &#8220;Prohibition has made nothing but trouble,&#8221; and &#8220;I am like any other man. All I do is supply a demand.&#8221; Acclaimed director delivers a thrillingly vivid slice of American outlaw history in his epic gangster tale, LAWLESS. LAWLESS is the true story of the infamous Bondurant Brothers: three bootlegging siblings who made a run for the American Dream in Prohibition-era Virginia. The film gathers an ensemble of gifted, dynamic new-generation stars &#8211; Tom Hardy, Shia LaBeouf, Jessica Chastain, Jason Clarke, Mia Wasikowska, Dane DeHaan &#8211; alongside two of the finest actors of their generations, Guy Pearce and Gary Oldman. A riveting, intense story of Crime and Corruption, Loyalty and Love, Brutality and Tenderness, LAWLESS is a rich addition to the American Gangster Canon.</desc><date>20260722</date><icon src="https://xstreamcp-assets-msp.streamready.in/assets/RUNNTV/PROGRAM/6a5f619a527eb6ddd76addc2/images/LANDSCAPE_169/5b722019-dcbf-4890-99d3-427e4d9b62